<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 12:45:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大多数美国人表示，当今的年轻人更难实现关键的财务里程碑</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/17/majorities-of-americans-say-key-financial-milestones-are-harder-for-todays-young-adults-to-reach/</link><description>大多数美国人表示，年轻人找工作、买房子、支付大学费用以及为未来储蓄比他们的父辈更难。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 01:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/17/majorities-of-americans-say-key-financial-milestones-are-harder-for-todays-young-adults-to-reach/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥人对克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆总统的好感度有所下降，但不如 2025 年</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/16/mexicans-view-president-claudia-sheinbaum-favorably-but-less-so-than-in-2025/</link><description>墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆仍然受欢迎，但她的好感度已降至 64%。对经济和民主的看法也在下降。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:27:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/16/mexicans-view-president-claudia-sheinbaum-favorably-but-less-so-than-in-2025/</guid></item><item><title>我们如何衡量美国人对公共生活的参与度</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/07/16/how-we-measured-americans-engagement-in-public-life/</link><description>本文解释了研究人员如何使用多模式调查、基于地址的抽样和聚类分析来衡量美国人对公共生活的参与度。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/07/16/how-we-measured-americans-engagement-in-public-life/</guid></item><item><title>美国人如何参与新闻、政治、宗教和公民生活</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/07/16/how-americans-are-engaged-with-news-politics-religion-and-civic-life/</link><description>美国人与他人的交往并不是一维的。相反，他们分为四个不同的群体，反映了不同的社会参与模式。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/07/16/how-americans-are-engaged-with-news-politics-religion-and-civic-life/</guid></item><item><title>现在许多国家的人们对中国的看法比美国更加积极</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/people-in-many-countries-now-view-china-more-positively-than-the-u-s/</link><description>最近，人们对中国的看法有所改善，而对美国的看法则有所恶化，目前大多数受访国家对中国的看法比美国更积极。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 01:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/people-in-many-countries-now-view-china-more-positively-than-the-u-s/</guid></item><item><title>全球对中国和习近平的看法正在改善</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/views-of-china-and-xi-are-improving-globally/</link><description>越来越多的人对中国抱有好感，对习近平充满信心，但富裕国家的看法却不那么积极。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/views-of-china-and-xi-are-improving-globally/</guid></item><item><title>党派关系情况说明书 (NPORS)</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/fact-sheet/party-affiliation-fact-sheet-npors/</link><description>使用皮尤研究中心全国民意参考调查 (NPORS) 的数据探索美国成年人党派认同的趋势。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2025 00:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/fact-sheet/party-affiliation-fact-sheet-npors/</guid></item><item><title>全国民意参考调查 (NPORS)</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/methods/fact-sheet/national-public-opinion-reference-survey-npors/</link><description>NPORS 是皮尤研究中心对美国成年人进行的年度调查，用于对多个主题进行基准估计。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2025 01:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/methods/fact-sheet/national-public-opinion-reference-survey-npors/</guid></item><item><title>近十分之六的年轻女性从影响者那里获取健康和保健信息</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/13/nearly-6-in-10-young-women-get-health-and-wellness-information-from-influencers/</link><description>年轻女性尤其可能表示，她们经常看到有影响力的关于美丽和外表的内容。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 01:17:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/13/nearly-6-in-10-young-women-get-health-and-wellness-information-from-influencers/</guid></item><item><title>美国人对以色列人的看法越来越负面，但对巴勒斯坦人的看法却相当稳定</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/09/americans-views-of-israelis-have-grown-increasingly-negative-but-views-of-palestinians-have-held-fairly-steady/</link><description>美国人对以色列人民和政府的看法在不同党派和年龄组中变得更加负面，而巴勒斯坦人的看法则基本保持稳定。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 01:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/09/americans-views-of-israelis-have-grown-increasingly-negative-but-views-of-palestinians-have-held-fairly-steady/</guid></item></channel></rss>